# Files executed inside Linux containers (bash scripts, Docker build files) must
# keep LF endings even on Windows checkouts. Without this, core.autocrlf=true
# rewrites them to CRLF on checkout, which breaks `bash` (`$'\r': command not
# found`) and Dockerfile line-continuations at build time.
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile* text eol=lf
entrypoint* text eol=lf
